data.title: Club, State & Region Directory
data.text:
The National Federation of Republican Women is organized at the local, state and regional levels:

At the local level, thousands of members are active in hundreds of Republican women's clubs.

Each state with at least two clubs has a state federation organization.

States are grouped into nine regions, each administered by a member of the national Executive Committee.

To access a Club, State or Region profile page (or to contact a Club, State or Region leader), use the directory below.
